<taskbody>
<steps>
<stepsection>To set preferences for <uicontrol>MVS Files</uicontrol>:</stepsection>
<step>
<cmd>In the <wintitle>Preferences</wintitle> window, navigate to <menucascade>
<uicontrol>Remote Systems</uicontrol>
<uicontrol>z/OS</uicontrol>
<uicontrol>MVS Files</uicontrol>
</menucascade> .</cmd>
</step>
